operator: Non-toy SPARC response operator R[n,g] = d chi2_holo(g) / d a_n (per galaxy)

basis.psi_normalization: projection uses discrete weighted coefficients on the solver z-grid; see diagnostics.projection.discrete

construction.perturbation: δφ(z)=±ε ψ_n(z); δA from linearized Hamiltonian constraint; gauge δA(z_min)=0

discrete.definition: c_m = Σ w_i δφ_i ψ_{m,i} / Σ w_i ψ_{m,i}^2, using i>=1 (discrete grid inner product)

continuous.definition: c_m = ∫ dz w(z) δφ(z) ψ_m(z) / ∫ dz w(z) ψ_m(z)^2 (trapz on the non-uniform z grid)
